“Someone came up behind me and said, ‘Do you know what your daughter is doing?’ I said ‘yes’ and went to get her,’” he said.
LaBelle angrily warned the pregnant woman.
“He said in an aggressive tone, ‘I shouldn’t have left your daughter near the door,’” Roseanna Monk said.
